港人應該3份2即刻自殺？<br />\n大把人無大學學歷應該死？？"},{"pid":"630feb97840f8faa8851ff9dcd49cbf9c85ce4cf","tid":530712,"uid":24160,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T10:00:55.000Z","msg":"政府目光窄<br />\n<br />\n成日想食老本<br />\n<br />\n靠金融服務業<br />\n<br />\n唔鼓勵人有創意思維<br />\n<br />\n再教育到工作每個細節同制度<br />\n<br />\n都係訓練奴性<br />\n<br />\n行業又單一<br />\n<br />\n唔係專科畢業食得屎<br />\n<br />\n想打份牛工都養唔到自己<br />\n<br />\n工時又長福利唔好<br />\n<br />\n冇其他才華唔讀就別無他選<br />\n<br />\n讀唔成, 半天吊就變地底泥<br />\n<br />\n再者, 物價高, 人工唔加<br />\n<br />\n根本成個政府上流人士有心營造一個奴隸社會出嚟<br />\n<br />\n要我地一生為奴<br />\n<br />\n為咗人生基本需要而拼命費時讀書<br />\n<br />\n消耗我地反抗極權嘅意志"},{"pid":"fa9bb0ce1d6dc73482bd68cd1d11d84084936231","tid":530712,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T10:03:52.000Z","msg":"全世界都係咁嫁啦，要生存做seven仔都可以。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5731072617527802b58069fce181ea8b20e9e75c","tid":530712,"uid":24160,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa9bb0ce1d6dc73482bd68cd1d11d84084936231","tid":530712,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T10:03:52.000Z","msg":"全世界都係咁嫁啦，要生存做seven仔都可以。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T10:22:00.000Z","msg":"五毛都喺校園台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}